":"","text_ayah":"\u0648\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0642\u064e\u062f\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0627\u0670\u0647\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0627\u064f\u0641\u064f\u0642\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0652\u0646\u0650\u06da ","text_id":"Sungguh, dia (Nabi Muhammad) benar-benar telah melihatnya (Jibril) di ufuk yang terang. ","text_en":"He had surely seen Him on the clear horizon.","transliteration":"wa laqad ra`āhu bil-ufuqil-mubīn","no_fn":"","text_fn":"","juz":30,"hizb":59,"rub_al_hizb":234,"page":586},{"id":5824,"surah":81,"no_ayah":24,"theme":"","text_ayah":"\u0648\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0647\u064f\u0648\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u063a\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0628\u0650 \u0628\u0650\u0636\u064e\u0646\u0650\u064a\u0652\u0646\u064d\u06da ","text_id":"Dia (Nabi Muhammad) bukanlah seorang yang kikir (enggan) untuk menerangkan yang gaib.","text_en":"He is not chary of making public what is unknown.","transliteration":"wa mā huwa 'alal-gaibi biḍanīn","no_fn":"","text_fn":"","juz":30,"hizb":59,"rub_al_hizb":234,"page":586},{"id":5825,"surah":81,"no_ayah":25,"theme":"","text_ayah":"\u0648\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0647\u064f\u0648\u064e \u0628\u0650\u0642\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0644\u0650 \u0634\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0637\u0670\u0646\u064d \u0631\u0651\u064e\u062c\u0650\u064a\u0652\u0645\u064d\u06da ","text_id":"(Al-Qur’an) itu bukanlah perkataan setan yang terkutuk.","text_en":"This is not the utterance of an accursed devil.","transliteration":"wa mā huwa biqauli syaiṭānir rajīm","no_fn":"","text_fn":"","juz":30,"hizb":59,"rub_al_hizb":234,"page":586},{"id":5826,"surah":81,"no_ayah":26,"theme":"","text_ayah":"\u0641\u064e\u0627\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u064e \u062a\u064e\u0630\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0648\u0652\u0646\u064e\u06d7 ","text_id":"Maka, ke manakah kamu akan pergi?<sup>747)</sup>","text_en":"So whither do you stray?","transliteration":"fa aina taż-habụn","no_fn":"747","text_fn":"747) Setelah diterangkan bahwa Al-